  "title": "Delivery Driver Class 3",
  "description": "<p>Flex Logistics is a fast growing Healthcare Logistics startup in Singapore.</p><p><em>For more details, please visit our website </em><a href=\"https://www.flexlogistics.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u>https://www.flexlogistics.sg/</u></a><em>.</em></p><p>We are in the hunt for a highly driven and motivated <u><strong>Operations Driver</strong></u> to join our highly talented team in a <strong>fast growing startup at the early stages of growth</strong>.</p><p><br /></p><ol><li><strong>Must possess valid Class 3 driving license</strong></li><li>Must be fit and able to lift max 20kg of goods independently (Short distance from lorry to trolley and vice versa)</li><li>Able to work independently and familiar with roads in Singapore</li><li>Do simple packing of top up consumables in preparation for delivery</li><li>Basic housekeeping for warehouse</li><li>Basic English needed</li><li>Working hours: Monday to Friday 8am-6pm</li><li>Saturday standby at home 8am -1230pm</li></ol><p><u><strong>ONLY APPLY THROUGH CAREERFUTURE OR EMAIL yiting.liew@flexlogistics.sg (WE DO NOT POST OUR JOB IN ANY OTHER PLATFORMS)</strong></u></p>",
